CREATE TABLE textbooks (
  textbook_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  title VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  author VARCHAR(50),
  publication_year INTEGER,
  quantity INTEGER
);

    category VARCHAR(50)
